text: Sander Arends and Tristan-Samuel Weissborn were the defending champions but chose not to defend their title. Jeevan Nedunchezhiyan and Franko Škugor won the title after defeating Rameez Junaid and Lukáš Rosol 6–3, 6–2 in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== * Main Draw Prosperita Open - Doubles 2017 Doubles
title: 2017 Prosperita Open – Doubles
